videos.description: C.J. Jackson drives for the layup to give the Buckeyes a seven-point advantage.
videos.headline: Ohio State's Jackson gets the tough layup to go

videos.description: Badgers' forward Nigel Hayes nails a tough turnaround jumper, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Hayes gets the and-1 for Wisconsin

videos.description: Jae'Sean Tate knocks down the circus shot for the basket and the foul.
videos.headline: Tate pads Ohio State's lead with the tough and-1

videos.description: Bronson Koenig knocks down the three near the end of the first half to become Wisconsin's leader in career 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Koenig breaks Badgers' record for three-pointers

videos.description: Badgers guard Kahlil Iverson drives the baseline on his way to the one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Iverson throws down the one-handed dunk

videos.description: Ohio State's mascot gives ESPN analyst Dan Dakich a hard time while calling Wisconsin-Ohio State.
videos.headline: Brutus messes around with Dan Dakich
